stateDiagram-v2
  [*] --> PENDING
  PENDING --> PUBLISHED: publish success
  PENDING --> RETRY: transient failure
  RETRY --> PUBLISHED: retry success
  RETRY --> FAILED: max retry exceeded
  PENDING --> SKIPPED: target NONE or disabled
  PENDING --> DRY_RUN: dryRun=true
  DRY_RUN --> PENDING: no external write
  PUBLISHED --> [*]
  FAILED --> [*]
  SKIPPED --> [*]

